snippet.title: PM Modi Condemns Rahul Gandhi’s Remarks On Hinduism; Sparks Uproar In Lok Sabha
snippet.description:
Rahul Gandhi Parliament Speech: In his first address in the 18th Lok Sabha, Congress MP Rahul Gandhi's comments led to pandemonium. Responding to the Motion of Thanks to the President’s Address, Rahul Gandhi remarked that "those who call themselves Hindus talk about violence," triggering an uproar. Prime Minister Narendra Modi and Home Minister Amit Shah intervened, demanding an apology for the serious allegations. Amidst slogans of "Modi" and "Bharat," Rahul Gandhi began with "Jai Samvidhan" and showcased "Abhay mudras" — the 'Hand' symbol of the Congress party — in various religious images, signifying fearlessness and non-violence.

#parliamentsession #rahulgandhi #amitshah #loksabhasession #parliament #loksabha

snippet.title: Indian Family and Foreigner  | Take A Break x @BhaDiPa
snippet.description:
Brace yourself for a comedy spectacle in our latest sketch, "Indian Family and Foreigner"! 😂🏡
In this side-splitting episode, we delve into the chaos that ensues when an Indian family plays host to a special guest – a Canadian colleague of the family's father. What starts as a simple visit quickly spirals into an uproarious whirlwind of cultural misunderstandings, hospitality overload, and neighborhood mayhem.
#LaughOutLoud #YouTubeSketch

It was a nice experience of working with Paula McGlynn from @BhaDiPa if you like this collab please let us know in comments.😇🙌

snippet.title: [HINDI] BGIS 2024 | GRAND FINALS | Day 1 | BGMI
snippet.description:
Welcome to the GRAND FINALS of the BGIS 2024

Feel the pulse-pounding intensity as the top 16 teams converge on the battleground for a shot at ultimate glory in BGIS history. This is more than just a tournament round, it's the climax of the BATTLEGROUNDS MOBILE INDIA SERIES 2024, where dreams soar and legends are made. With a massive prize pool of INR 2 Crores, the stakes are at their peak.

16 Lan Finalists: GLOBAL ESPORTS, TEAM AARU, X SPARK, iQOO SOUL, FS ESPORTS, VASISTA ESPORTS, TEAM TAMILAS, R4VEN ESPORTS, CARNIVAL GAMING, MOGO ESPORTS, TEAM LIMRA, VENOM GAMING, 8 BIT, TEAM INSANE ESPORTS, INFERNO SQUAD, RECKONING ESPORTS.


#MAKEWAVES #BATTLEGROUNDSMOBILEINDIA #INDIAKAGAME #RISEABOVE

snippet.title: Rakesh Barot | નઈ બને તારે મારે | Nai Bane Tare Mare | 2024 New Gujarati Song | નવું ગુજરાતી ગીત
snippet.description:
Groove to the upbeat tunes of Rakesh Barot's new Gujarati song "નઈ બને તારે મારે," available now on @SaregamaGujarati 

Singer: Rakesh Barot
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema
Singer: Rakesh Barot
Artist: Rakesh Barot,Sudha Tripathi
Music: Rahul Nadiya , Ravi Nagar
Lyrics: Vipul Raval
Creative Head : Dhyey Films & Team
DOP-Editing: Chirag kachhadiya 
Production: Satubha. 
Spot: Raju n akshay 
Choreographer: Dipak turi 
Concept n director: Pranav jethva 
Technically Support: Jenish Talaviya
Hair makeup: Hasmukh 
Light: Kalpesh jadav

તુ મને બાળવા  ફરે  જાનુ બીજાની હારે …(૨)
તું આવું રે કરી ખોટા  દેખાવ કેમ કરે …
અરે જા ઠગાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે જા જૂઠાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે ખોટા ખેલ ચમ તું કરે ,મને ફેર કઈ નઈ પડે (૨)
અરે જા ઠગાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે જા જૂઠાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે
તારા જેવી છોડીયો મને સત્તર રે ભડકોની ,
મારા શોમુ ઇનુ ઉતરી ગિયું છે પોની ,
ઓ તુ મને પડવા ફરે એવુ કોઈ કાળે નહીં થાવનું ,
ઉતરી જરે અભિમાન તારે મોપ માં રહેવાનું ..
ભલે તું મને હેરાન કરે મારી પાછળ પાછળ ફરે (૨)
અરે જા ઠગાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે જા જૂઠાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
ઓ મને  ને ભાળી તું તો નખરા ઘણા કરે ,
તને એમ લગતું હશે મારા પર મરે છે ,
ઓ તારો ઠાઠ નજારો જોઈ હું પીગળી નહિ જવાનો ,
તારી પાછળ હુ ગોંડો નહિ થાવનો ,
તને હું પડીશ બહુ ભારે ,તુ જતી રે તારા ઘરે ,(૨)
અરે જા ઠગાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે જા જૂઠાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,(2)

Jaan Nisar Episode 26 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Danish Taimoor - Hiba Bukhari - Haroon Shahid - 30th June 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Mohsin Mirza
Writer: Rehana Aftab

Cast:

snippet.title: Dhilluku Dhuddu - Comedy Scenes | Santhanam Super Hit Counters | Adithya TV
snippet.description:
Kumar and Kajal are in love but her father is against the match and tries to have Kumar killed with the help of Mani. Things go awry when Mani invites Kumar's family to a haunted house. 

Dhilluku Dhuddu  is a 2016 Indian Tamil-language comedy horror film directed by Rambala and produced by Sri Thenandal Films. The film features starring Santhanam and Anchal Singh in the leading roles, while Saurabh Shukla appears in a pivotal role. Featuring music composed by S. Thaman, Dhilluku Dhuddu began production in November 2015 and released on 7 July 2016 to positive response and turned to be successful at box office.[3][4][5] The film was later dubbed in Hindi as Raj Mahal 3 in 2017. The film was dubbed in Telugu as Dammunte Sommera in 2018.[6] The film was remade in Kannada in 2019 as Gimmick starring Ganesh.

They are a great addition to your beauty routine and help get you smooth and buttery skin

snippet.title: பாறை மீன் குழம்பும் பாஸ்மதி அரிசி சோறும்!| Amma Makes Traditional Fish Curry with Dubar Basmati Rice
snippet.description:
அப்பா பிடித்து குடுத்த மீனை வைத்து அம்மா இன்று பாசுமதி அரிசி சோறுடன், பாறை மீன் குழம்பு வைத்து  குடுத்தாங்க.

 சுவாரஸ்யமா இன்று பாயசமும் பாசுமதி அரிசியில செஞ்சு குடுத்தாங்க.

பாசுமதி அரிசியை எப்படி பயன்படுத்தணும்னு அம்மா இந்த வீடியோல விளக்கமா சொல்றாங்க, இந்தியாகேட் பாஸ்மதி அரிசிய வச்சு இதேமாதிரி உங்களுக்குப் பிடிச்ச உணவு வகைகளையும் செய்து பார்க்கலாம். நீங்களும் உங்கள் வீட்டில் முயற்சி செய்தால் கமெண்டில் எங்களுக்கு தெரியப்படுத்தவும்!

#experimentswithbasmati #indiagatefoods

snippet.title: Stepaa Maar Song Tomorrow  | Double ISMART | RAmPothineni | Puri Jagannadh| Charmme Kaur
snippet.description:
Seeti Maar shots straight from the sets 🤙
Get ready for the Sensational #STEPPAMAAR to take over the Masses with a Bang 💥

Double ISMART First Single out Tomorrow at 4 PM 🎶🔥

#DoubleISMART is an Indian Action Entertainer film, written and directed by Puri Jagannnadh featuring Ram Pothineni in the lead role will be seen in a Massier character than iSmart Shankar. Also stars Sanjay Dutt, Kavya Thapar in the prominent roles. Produced by Puri Jagannadh and Charmme Kaur under Puri Connects, The film will have a much bigger span and will be made with a high budget on a large scale with top-class technical standards. Double iSmart will be releasing worldwide on AUGUST 15th,2024  in Telugu, Tamil, Kannada, Malayalam, and Hindi languages.

Movie Details:
Cast: Ram Pothineni, Sanjay Dutt, Kavya Thapar, Bani J, Ali, Getup Sreenu, Sayaji Shinde, Makrand Deshpande,  Temper Vamsi & others.
Writer, Director: Puri Jagannadh
Producers: Puri Jagannadh, Charmme Kaur
Banner: Puri Connects 
Music: Manisharma 
CEO: Vish

#saasuaala #rahuldhandlaniya #sonikadhandlaniya #ashumorkhi #sarwangmusic #haryanvi #haryanvisong #haryanvidjsongs2024 #haryanvisongsharyanavi #djsong 

👉 Song Lyrics ----
कोन्या चाहिए र लुगाई 
तने घुट मिल जा
मेरी सासु आला मैंने 
 घना उत्त मिलग्या,
मेरी सासु आला मैंने
घना उत्त मिल्ग्या,

तेरे टेक्कू रहप्टे
तु इसे काम ना करे,
र मैं कोनी पिंदा दारु
बदनाम ना करे,
र मैं कोनी पिंदा जान
बदनाम ना करे,

हो मैंने बेवड़ा मिला स
र ना फोजी थानेदार,
फेर पोये जाइए रोटी
तने छोडु भरतार,
तेरा मेरा बता क्योंकर
सुत मिलग्या,
हो मेरी सासु आला
मैंने घना उत्त मिलग्या,
मेरी सासु आला मैंने
घना उत्त मिलग्या,

हो रोज लाड़ ना लड़ाते
मखा फाेजी थानेदार,
छोरा घना हैंडसम
खानदानी घरबार,
तोली तोली रोटी पोले
र तु घाम ना करे,
र मैं कोन्या पिंदा दारू
बदनाम ना करे,
र मैं कोन्या पिंदा जान
बदनाम ना करे,

प्रीतम शर्मा सुन रोज
तेरे आवे स उलहाने,
गाम डुडीआले म तु
रोज लिखे जा स गाने,
आशु मोरखी आला
कसूत मिलग्या,
मेरी सासु आला
मैंने घना उत्त मिलग्या,
मेरी सासु आला
मैंने घना उत्त मिलग्या,

र उलहाना न तु छोड़
तेरी रीझ मैं पुगा दु,
गुठी डायमंड आली चार
कोका नाक का घड़वा दु,
जमा रानी की ज्यु रहिए
बेशक काम ना करे,
र मैं कोन्या पिंदा दारू
बदनाम ना करे,
र मैं कोन्या पिंदा जान
बदनाम ना करे,

Keep Supporting us with your Love, Like, Comments, Share & must Subscribe our Channel.

snippet.title: Sipahi  - Amit Bhadana - Official Full Movie
snippet.description:
Rate Sipahi on IMDB - https://www.imdb.com/title/tt32765621/

This special film showcases the struggle of Sanatan Vijay, a poor boy aspiring to join the police force as a constable. Dedicated to the hardworking youth of the nation who dare to dream, 'Sipahi' aims to uncover their struggle and inspire everyone. Through Sanatan Vijay's story, the film celebrates resilience and determination, making it a poignant tribute to those who strive to overcome their circumstances and achieve their dreams.

snippet.description:
'Kalki 2898 AD' hit the theatres worldwide on June 27. Led by Prabhas, the sci-fi thriller boasts of a stellar cast including Amitabh Bachchan, Deepika Padukone and Kamal Haasan. The Nag Ashwin directorial took a mammoth opening at the box office and has scripted history by becoming the third biggest opener in Indian cinema as it has earned Rs 180 crore worldwide according to early estimates by industry tracker Sacnilk.com. The makers have reported 191.5 crores.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.description:

Gopal ventures into farming and producing vegetables. But will Maharaj be okay with his venture?

Show Name: Gopal Bhar - গোপাল ভর
Directed By: Sourav Mondal, Hansa Mondal
Written By: Hansa Mondal
Original language:  Bengali
Episode No: 1062

#GopalBhar #sonyaath #গোপালভর 

About Gopal Bhar:
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him as a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta.
